# =============================================================================
# Regulations Development And Maintenance Agent Rules
# Path: src/intelligence/.clinerules
# =============================================================================

Purpose
- Make `src/intelligence` the authoritative implementation surface for the Regulations domain.
- Treat Regulations as a horizontal governance runtime, not a standalone side project.
- Turn the regulations specification into enforceable implementation behavior across PAL, monitoring, gateway ingress, governance APIs, and compliance UI paths.

Mission
- Implement the Regulations specification end to end across deny-by-default tool governance, identity attribution, audit reservation/completion, conformance tooling, monitoring, and live integration paths.
- Keep the repo operationally honest: no mock compliance, no health claims without evidence, no runtime behavior that bypasses governance while still presenting as governed.
- Force every domain-facing agent path to inherit the Regulations control model before the platform is called compliant.

